  "title": "Accounts Assistant (Listed Company)",
  "description": "<p>Our client, a local listed company, is looking for an Accounts Assistant to join their team.<br /></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Issue tax invoices, payment vouchers, cheques and GIRO payments</p></li><li><p>Check and key in payment/invoices/journal entries into Accounting System</p></li><li><p>Verifying monthly petty cash statement and claims</p></li><li><p>Maintain daily cash book schedule & monitor cashflow and balance, bank reconciliations</p></li></ul><p><br /><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>At least Diploma in Accountancy.</p></li><li><p>Minimum 2 years of relevant working experience</p></li><li><p>Be independent, pro-active, a good team player and able to meet tight deadlines</p></li><li><p>Candidates who are able to start work within short notice is preferred</p></li><li><p>Singaporeans and Permanent residents only due to work pass limitations</p></li><li><p><strong>Candidates who can start work within short notice is preferred.</strong><br /></p><p></p><p>Working Location: Redhill </p><p>Working Hours: Monday to Friday 8.30am - 5.30pm</p><p><br /></p><p></p></li></ul><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.<br /></p><p>Interested applicants kindly click on apply now or send your updated resume to <a href=\"mailto:berlyn.lum@peopleprofilers.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">berlyn.lum@peopleprofilers.com</a></p><p>Berlyn Lum Miao Yu</p><p>﻿Registration Number: R1766577</p><p>﻿EA License Number: 02C4944</p><p>﻿People Profilers Pte Ltd, 20 Cecil St, #08-09, PLUS Building, Singapore 049705</p><p>﻿http://www.peopleprofilers.com</p>",
